title: Squeem - Perfectly Curvy, Women's Firm Control Strapless Waist Cincher
description:
75% Natural Rubber 25% Cotton
CURVE CREATING WITH COMFORT: The strapless waist cincher offers incredible waist shaping and tummy control, without compromising comfort. It sheds inches from the midsection area and enhances your natural curves, immediately after putting it on, helping you feel sexy and comfortable all day long. If you are a new mom, Squeem is the ONLY cincher you'll actually want to wear on postpartum recovery.
DISCREET UNDER CLOTHES: The most discreet high compression shapewear you will ever try. Wear it under any dress, skirt, or top without giving away your secret. Feel more confident with your own curvy body.
IMPROVED POSTURE: Squeem Perfectly Curvy Waist Cincher's unique design and internal flexible steel bones offer amazing back support and improve posture while moderately lifting the breasts.

The premium waist cincher comfortably contours the midsection, with a boned stainless steel interior for superior support and posture. We have been re-envisioning women's shapewear from an unmistakably Brazilian point of view, upholding a tradition of quality and attention to detail since 1936.
HOW DO I WEAR MY SQUEEM? Perfectly Curvy Waist Cincher is a corset-style braless waist-cincher that instantly reduces inches from your waist. Wear it under that sexy backless party dress, or even to define your silhouette under your favorite strapless tank top. The double row hook & eye offers adjustable compression levels to a perfect fit. It's sleek surface guarantees it won't stick to your garments. A smooth finishing reduces visible lines. Also perfect for maternity postpartum belly wrap.

INSTANT & ACCURATE READINGS – Once luggage weight has been determined, the scale will beep to instantly reveal precise, easy-to-read measurements on the large backlit LCD display.
ADVANCED FEATURES – Checking more than one bag? Simply press the scale’s ON/OFF button to reset and continue weighing. Built-in Auto Calibration ensures consistently accurate readings, while the 20-second Auto Off feature conserves battery life.
100% SATISFACTION – Customer satisfaction is our highest priority. If this travel scale doesn’t meet your standards, we’ll replace it for you! A 2-year and 1 CR2032 battery are included.

?NATURAL LOOK: A demi cup bra has cups that only cover about half of the bust. They are cut low across the whole cup, as opposed to a plunge bra, which is only low in the center, resulting in an overall more natural look. This style is very popular for designer lingerie and well suited for lace details.
?LESS VISIBILITY: An unlined bra is essentially a bra that only has one piece of fabric across the bust and is less visible under clothing. The great thing about unlined bras is that they still offer support without the extra weight and bulk of too much padding. As a result, they feel lightweight and comfortable, and because they show more of the natural form, they also feel sexy in a very subtle way.
?MYSTERIOUS, ALLURING & SOPHISTICATED: The chantilly lace overlay and unlined design adds a hint of sexiness, while still looking feminine and sophisticated. Add sultry intrigue underneath that little black dress or V-neck tee for a million dollar look. The fabric content of the item is 83% Nylon and 17% Spandex / Mesh: 69% Nylon and 31% Spandex.
?HIGH QUALITY FABRIC: Composed of a nylon fabric and spandex mesh with a stretch chantilly lace overlay, this bra encompasses comfortability, stretchiness and overall femininity. Plush back padded straps have also been added for additional comfort.
?CHOOSE FELINA: For over 30 years, Felina has perfected what women want in intimate apparel, offering unique styles while ensuring affordability and a perfect fit. Our mission is to bring about the very best in every woman. SIZING: Runs Full Size Large. Order one size down. Click on the "Size Chart" icon to ensure correct sizing before purchasing. Wear the same type of sock to the that you’ll be wearing with the particular shoe. Width is often as important as length, so make sure the shoe fits in every direction. If you fall in love with a pair that’s slightly too big, try them on with insoles. If your feet are different sizes, make sure to measure the larger one for best fit.
FITMENT: Moccasins should fit snugly without feeling uncomfortable. Over time they will stretch to the contours of your foot and wear pattern. If you are unsure about the fit, slide an index finger behind your heel. If it doesn’t fit, go a size up. If it slides into the shoe easily, you should probably drop a half- to full-size.
STELLAR BEST SELLER: There’s a reason the handmade Kilty moc is our most popular moccasin. Its sleek design is fashion forward, yet practical and oh-so comfortable. Slip your feet into these supple suede leather shoes with ultra-flexible bottoms and you can go all day. With a variety of colors to choose from, these moccasins will match any look in your closet. Or pick a pair in every hue, a special treat just for you.
COMFORT & DURABILITY: We use quality materials for a luxurious look and feel. Suede leather, moosehide, and deerskin are silky soft to step into while still providing durable support. Horween leather provides our custom driving mocs with high-end, luxury full grain aniline, and our first-rate sheepskin lining is cozy and soft while still allowing feet to breath.
CRAFTMENSHIP: Since 1946 we’ve crafted moccasin style footwear, and we’ve still stayed true to our roots. Always real, our rich heritage includes a tradition of careful craftsmanship to deliver exceptional footwear. We use the finest materials to ensure comfort, durability, and timeless style. Whether you are buying your first pair of Minnetonka moccasins or have been with us for years of iconic looks, we welcome you to be a part of our story.
